Small fixxes/tweakings done and release the final v1

Tweakings V1_1

# De deagle glitch in the knife only round is fixxed.
# Extra knife equip added in extra case (for the end).
# All players on the ending will get 100HP.
# Secret hints added for trap 2.
# Clip brushes added on some spots to avoid players getting stuck.
# FINAL version as everything should work fine now.

Tweakings V1

# Songs are placed to the end, they dont play the entire map anymore.
# DJ is gone because of the song changes.
# CT's dont die at the end anymore, they get teleported to.
# CT's who are not a winner, will only get a deagle in the battle.
# 2 new extra songs added on request.
# 1 fun sound at spawn added. ("Ok lets go").
# Complete final stable version 1.
